{"tid":740653,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"洛夫雲：我是『世界上最好的後衛之一』","createTime":"2018-07-13T04:55:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T17:01:23.000Z","uid":54344,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e3fc30811938bcae11a8951938dd69afaae0127b","tid":740653,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T04:55:49.000Z","msg":"World Cup 2018: Liverpool&rsquo;s Dejan Lovren claims he is &lsquo;one of the best defenders in the world&rsquo; after helping Croatia beat England<br />\n<br />\n&quot;I showed why I took Liverpool to the final of the Champions League and now with the national team, and now I&rsquo;m in the World Cup final.<br />\n<br />\nI think people should recognise that I&rsquo;m one of the best defenders in the world.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n『我今年帶著利物浦進入冠軍聯賽決賽，現在我和國家隊一起進入了世界杯決賽。<br />\n<br />\n我認為人們應該承認我是世界上最好的後衛之一。』<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/world-cup-2018/6759463/world-cup-2018-liverpool-dejan-lovren/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fworld-cup-2018%2F6759463%2Fworld-cup-2018-liverpool-dejan-lovren%2F&d=D2YYfmw9pscn5chN2XgR%2BiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=e03b25d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thesun.co.uk/world-cup-2018/6759463/world-cup-2018-liverpool-dejan-lovren/</a><br />\n<br />\n笑撚到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39d33a63247576ba72dfc450966357cfa981576","tid":740653,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T04:58:06.000Z","msg":"all in 法國<br />\ncall定agent星期一睇樓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a53d01cb99541fa6b90f4113cbe27181772c558","tid":740653,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T05:01:48.000Z","msg":"I show